{"tid":2326951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師的責任不是打官司　而是給予市民合法性","createTime":"2020-12-15T16:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T03:23:09.000Z","uid":261647,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a78c5cf0358ffe1a0fc0b95c92b8ba75576af85f","tid":2326951,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158324543112357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158324543112357&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=316fe77b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158324543112357</a><br />\n<br />\n合法的是我們，我們為了保衛自己故鄉做的行為都是合法的。非法的是對方，他們為了搶奪香港財產，以及維護自己的特權，在香港設立的法律和制度都是非法的。這個基礎都沒有確立，反而指保衛故鄉是非法的，佔領者是合法的，律師以為自己的責任是打官司，而不是給予市民合法性，讀了那麼多法律真的是讀屎片。"},{"pid":"d453a76405be07a49e3072402b67df332971a51f","tid":2326951,"uid":263648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a78c5cf0358ffe1a0fc0b95c92b8ba75576af85f","tid":2326951,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158324543112357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158324543112357&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=316fe77b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158324543112357</a><br />\n<br />\n合法的是我們，我們為了保衛自己故鄉做的行為都是合法的。非法的是對方，他們為了搶奪香港財產，以及維護自己的特權，在香港設立的法律和制度都是非法的。這個基礎都沒有確立，反而指保衛故鄉是非法的，佔領者是合法的，律師以為自己的責任是打官司，而不是給予市民合法性，讀了那麼多法律真的是讀屎片。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:36:29.000Z","msg":"律師只係提供法律風險既意見、同埋盡力保障法律權利。<br />\n<br />\n做唔做，係個客自己決定。"},{"pid":"8c2263f04411ab08789ec7bad9b105a8838d6a9d","tid":2326951,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiiENAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum